s%20to%20a%20real%20person.%20If%20those%20people%20get%20angry%20at%20you%20or%20sic%20law%20enforcement%20on%20you%2C%20that's%20all%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%0A%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%3EPrivacy%20and%20Cookie%20Notice%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EI%20will%20%3Ci%3Enot%3C%2Fi%3E%20collect%20any%20identifying%20information%20about%20you.%20No%20Google%20Analytics%2C%20nothing.%20I%2C%20the%20site%20owner%2C%20value%20your%20privacy%20as%20much%20as%20mine.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20guestbook%20uses%20HTML%20Comment%20Box%2C%20it%20may%20leave%20cookies%20on%20your%20computer.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20these%20cookies%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20deleting%20them.%20I%20suggest%20you%20read%20HTML%20Comment%20Box's%20privacy%20policy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.htmlcommentbox.com%2Fstatic%2Fprivacy.pdf%22%3Ehere.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Also%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20using%20extensions%20that%20block%20trackers%20in%20%5Binsert%20current%20year%20here%5D%2C%20then%20what%20the%20%3Ci%3Efuck%3C%2Fi%3E%20are%20you%20doing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20get%20a%20cookie%20just%20for%20visiting%20the%20site.%20This%20is%20normal%2C%20many%20sites%20do%20this%2C%20and%20my%20site%20does%20this%20since%20it's%20hosted%20by%20Neocities.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20want%20this%20cookie%20on%20your%20machine%2C%20I%20suggest%20either%20blocking%20or%20removing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20as%20a%20fair%20warning%2C%20I%20have%20allowed%20all%20permissions%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%22%3EInternet%20Archive%3C%2Fa%3E's%20bot%20in%20this%20site's%20robots.txt%20file.%20This%20means%20that%20this%20website%20can%20(and%20will)%20be%20logged%20into%20the%20IA's%20Wayback%20Machine.%20The%20IA%20is%20a%20very%20important%20organization%20that%20is%20dear%20to%20my%20heart%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I'm%20comfortable%20with%20their%20bot%20crawling%20my%20pages%20for%20archiving%20purposes.%20If%20this%20makes%20you%20uncomfortable%2C%20then%20I%20suggest%20not%20signing%20the%20guest%20book%2C%20or%20at%20least%20not%20using%20your%20real%20name%20or%20current%20Internet%20handle%20when%20signing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%3EWhy%20the%20Hell%20Does%20This%20Site%20Exist%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20project%20of%20one%20very%20bored%202000's%20kid%20nostalgic%20for%20the%20shittily-made%20GeoCities%20sites%20of%20the%2090's%20and%20early%202000's.%20Don't%20get%20me%20wrong%2C%20I%20love%20modern%20web%20design.%20It's%20so%20smooth%2C%20calming%2C%20and%20aesthetically%20pleasing.%20It's%20amazing%20how%20web%20design's%20evolved%20over%20the%20Internet's%20lifespan.%20However%2C%20I'm%20drawn%20to%20those%20homemade%2C%20free%20websites%20from%20the%20ye%20olden%20days.%20They've%20got%20a%20charm%20to%20their%20shittiness%2C%20really.%20It%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Internet%20was%20new%20and%20exciting%20and%20everyone%20with%20a%20modem%20wanted%20to%20mark%20their%20place%20on%20the%20web%2C%20even%20if%20they%20knew%20next%20to%20nothing%20about%20web%20design.%20The%20sheer%20shittiness%20is%20art%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20harken%20back%20to%20the%20GeoCities%20websites%20of%20yore.%20Where%20your%20average%20Internet%20user%20had%20unbridled%20creativity%2C%20crap%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20a%20free%20hosting%20service%20at%20their%20disposal.%20This%20site%20is%20%3Ci%3Emeant%3C%2Fi%3E%20to%20look%20shitty%20and%20make%20your%20eyes%20bleed.%20I'm%20not%20using%20that%20as%20a%20cop-out%2C%20I'm%20being%20serious.%20I%20just%20want%20my%20creativity%20to%20flow%20and%20add%20whatever%20the%20hell%20I%20want%2C%20just%20like%20people%20did%20in%20the%2090's%20and%202000's.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETL%3BDR%3A%20Personal%20art%20project%2Fshitpost%20with%20webcore%20themes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%3EAlso%2C%20Why%20the%20Phone%20Themes%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20inspired%20by%20classic%20forum%20spam%20and%20malicious%20ads.%20More%20recurring%20themes%20are%20probably%20going%20to%20pop%20up%2C%20this%20is%20a%20continuing%20work%20in%20progress%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%3EIs%20This%20Part%20of%20an%20ARG%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENO.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20it%20is%2C%20%20%3Ci%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3EI%20did%20not%20give%20permission%20for%20the%20ARG%20creator%20to%20do%20this!%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20If%20you're%20a%20visitor%20who%20plans%20on%20using%20my%20shitty%20site%20for%20your%20shitty%20ARG%2C%20turn%20away%2C%20this%20ain't%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fdialup-kween.neocities.org%2Fmysterypage.html%22%20style%3D%22color%3Awhite%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20id%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Best%20viewed%20with%20%3Cimg%3E%20and%20%3Cimg%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch3%20style%3D%22color%3Awhite%3B%20text-align%3Acenter%3B%22%3E%20Not%20copyrighted%20%C2%A9%202020%20dialup-kween%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fdialup-kween.neocities.org%2Fsitemap.html%22%3ESite%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
